5656  VALUE v = OPERAND_AT(iobj, j);
5657  rb_str_concat(str, opobj_inspect(v));
5658  break;
5659  }
5660  case TS_ID: /* ID */
5661  rb_str_concat(str, opobj_inspect(OPERAND_AT(iobj, j)));
5662  break;
5663  case TS_GENTRY:
5664  {
5665  struct rb_global_entry *entry = (struct rb_global_entry *)
5666  (OPERAND_AT(iobj, j) & (~1));
5667  rb_str_append(str, rb_id2str(entry->id));
5668  break;
5669  }
5670  case TS_IC: /* inline cache */
5671  rb_str_catf(str, "<ic:%d>", FIX2INT(OPERAND_AT(iobj, j)));
5672  break;
5673  case TS_CALLINFO: /* call info */
5674  {
5675  rb_call_info_t *ci = (rb_call_info_t *)OPERAND_AT(iobj, j);
5676  rb_str_cat2(str, "<callinfo:");
5677  if (ci->mid)
5678  rb_str_catf(str, "%"PRIsVALUE, rb_id2str(ci->mid));
5679  rb_str_catf(str, ", %d>", ci->orig_argc);
5680  break;
5681  }
5682  case TS_CDHASH: /* case/when condition cache */
5683  rb_str_cat2(str, "<ch>");
5684  break;
5685  case TS_FUNCPTR:
5686  {
5687  rb_insn_func_t func = (rb_insn_func_t)OPERAND_AT(iobj, j);
5688 #ifdef HAVE_DLADDR
5689  Dl_info info;
5690  if (dladdr(func, &info) && info.dli_sname) {
5691  rb_str_cat2(str, info.dli_sname);
5692  break;
5693  }
5694 #endif
5695  rb_str_catf(str, "<%p>", func);
5696  }
5697  break;
5698  default:{
5699  rb_raise(rb_eSyntaxError, "unknown operand type: %c", type);
5700  }
5701  }
5702  if (types[j + 1]) {
5703  rb_str_cat2(str, ", ");
5704  }
5705  }
5706  }
5707  return str;
5708 }

6118  iseq->param.keyword->required_num++;

6122  default_len = len - i;
6123  if (default_len == 0) {
6124  return;
6125  }
6126

6128

6131  CHECK_ARRAY(key);
6132 
6133  switch (RARRAY_LEN(key)) {
6134  case 1:
6135  sym = RARRAY_AREF(key, 0);
6136  default_val = Qundef;
6137  break;
6138  case 2:
6139  sym = RARRAY_AREF(key, 0);
6140  default_val = RARRAY_AREF(key, 1);
6141  break;
6142  default:
6143  rb_raise(rb_eTypeError,
6144  "keyword default has unsupported len %+"PRIsVALUE,
6145  key);
6146  }
6147  iseq->param.keyword->table[i] = SYM2ID(sym);
6148  iseq->param.keyword->default_values[j] = default_val;
6149  }

3719  while (ip) {
3720  if (!ip->compile_data) {
3721  ip = 0;
3722  break;
3723  }
3724 
3725  level++;
3726  if (ip->compile_data->redo_label != 0) {
3727  level = 0x8000;
3728  if (ip->compile_data->loopval_popped == 0) {
3729  /* need value */
3730  level |= 0x4000;
3731  }
3732  goto break_by_insn;
3733  }
3734  else if (ip->type == ISEQ_TYPE_BLOCK) {
3735  level <<= 16;
3736  goto break_by_insn;
3737  }
3738  else if (ip->type == ISEQ_TYPE_EVAL) {
3739  goto break_in_eval;
3740  }
3741 
3742  ip = ip->parent_iseq;
3743  }
3744  COMPILE_ERROR((ERROR_ARGS "Invalid break"));
3745  }
3746  break;
3747  }
3748  case NODE_NEXT:{
3749  unsigned long level = 0;
3750 
3751  if (iseq->compile_data->redo_label != 0) {
3752  LABEL *splabel = NEW_LABEL(0);
3753  debugs("next in while loop\n");
3754  ADD_LABEL(ret, splabel);
3755  COMPILE(ret, "next val/valid syntax?", node->nd_stts);
3756  add_ensure_iseq(ret, iseq, 0);
3757  ADD_ADJUST(ret, line, iseq->compile_data->redo_label);
3758  ADD_INSNL(ret, line, jump, iseq->compile_data->start_label);
3759  ADD_ADJUST_RESTORE(ret, splabel);
3760  if (!poped) {
3761  ADD_INSN(ret, line, putnil);
3762  }
3763  }
3764  else if (iseq->compile_data->end_label) {
3765  LABEL *splabel = NEW_LABEL(0);
3766  debugs("next in block\n");
3767  ADD_LABEL(ret, splabel);
3768  ADD_ADJUST(ret, line, iseq->compile_data->start_label);
3769  COMPILE(ret, "next val", node->nd_stts);
3770  add_ensure_iseq(ret, iseq, 0);
3771  ADD_INSNL(ret, line, jump, iseq->compile_data->end_label);
3772  ADD_ADJUST_RESTORE(ret, splabel);
3773 
3774  if (!poped) {
3775  ADD_INSN(ret, line, putnil);
3776  }
3777  }
3778  else if (iseq->type == ISEQ_TYPE_EVAL) {
3779  next_in_eval:
3780  COMPILE_ERROR((ERROR_ARGS "Can't escape from eval with next"));
3781  }
3782  else {
3783  rb_iseq_t *ip;
3784  ip = iseq;
3785  while (ip) {
3786  if (!ip->compile_data) {
3787  ip = 0;
3788  break;
3789  }
3790 
3791  level = 0x8000 | 0x4000;
3792  if (ip->compile_data->redo_label != 0) {
3793  /* while loop */
3794  break;
3795  }
3796  else if (ip->type == ISEQ_TYPE_BLOCK) {
3797  break;
3798  }
3799  else if (ip->type == ISEQ_TYPE_EVAL) {
3800  goto next_in_eval;
3801  }
3802 
3803  ip = ip->parent_iseq;
3804  }
3805  if (ip != 0) {
3806  COMPILE(ret, "next val", node->nd_stts);
3807  ADD_INSN1(ret, line, throw, INT2FIX(level | 0x03) /* TAG_NEXT */ );
3808 
3809  if (poped) {
3810  ADD_INSN(ret, line, pop);
3811  }
3812  }
3813  else {
3814  COMPILE_ERROR((ERROR_ARGS "Invalid next"));
3815  }
3816  }
3817  break;
3818  }
3819  case NODE_REDO:{
3820  if (iseq->compile_data->redo_label) {
3821  LABEL *splabel = NEW_LABEL(0);
3822  debugs("redo in while");
3823  ADD_LABEL(ret, splabel);
3824  ADD_ADJUST(ret, line, iseq->compile_data->redo_label);
3825  add_ensure_iseq(ret, iseq, 0);
3826  ADD_INSNL(ret, line, jump, iseq->compile_data->redo_label);
3827  ADD_ADJUST_RESTORE(ret, splabel);
3828  if (!poped) {
3829  ADD_INSN(ret, line, putnil);
3830  }
3831  }
3832  else if (iseq->type == ISEQ_TYPE_EVAL) {
3833  redo_in_eval:
3834  COMPILE_ERROR((ERROR_ARGS "Can't escape from eval with redo"));
3835  }
3836  else if (iseq->compile_data->start_label) {
3837  LABEL *splabel = NEW_LABEL(0);
3838 
3839  debugs("redo in block");
3840  ADD_LABEL(ret, splabel);
3841  add_ensure_iseq(ret, iseq, 0);
3842  ADD_ADJUST(ret, line, iseq->compile_data->start_label);
3843  ADD_INSNL(ret, line, jump, iseq->compile_data->start_label);
3844  ADD_ADJUST_RESTORE(ret, splabel);
3845 
3846  if (!poped) {
3847  ADD_INSN(ret, line, putnil);
3848  }
3849  }
3850  else {
3851  rb_iseq_t *ip;
3852  unsigned long level;
3853  level = 0x8000 | 0x4000;
3854  ip = iseq;
3855  while (ip) {
3856  if (!ip->compile_data) {
3857  ip = 0;
3858  break;
3859  }
3860 
3861  if (ip->compile_data->redo_label != 0) {
3862  break;
3863  }
3864  else if (ip->type == ISEQ_TYPE_BLOCK) {
3865  break;
3866  }
3867  else if (ip->type == ISEQ_TYPE_EVAL) {
3868  goto redo_in_eval;
3869  }
3870 
3871  ip = ip->parent_iseq;
3872  }
3873  if (ip != 0) {
3874  ADD_INSN(ret, line, putnil);
3875  ADD_INSN1(ret, line, throw, INT2FIX(level | 0x05) /* TAG_REDO */ );
3876 
3877  if (poped) {
3878  ADD_INSN(ret, line, pop);
3879  }
3880  }
3881  else {
3882  COMPILE_ERROR((ERROR_ARGS "Invalid redo"));
3883  }
3884  }
3885  break;
3886  }
3887  case NODE_RETRY:{
3888  if (iseq->type == ISEQ_TYPE_RESCUE) {
3889  ADD_INSN(ret, line, putnil);
3890  ADD_INSN1(ret, line, throw, INT2FIX(0x04) /* TAG_RETRY */ );
3891 
3892  if (poped) {
3893  ADD_INSN(ret, line, pop);
3894  }
3895  }
3896  else {
3897  COMPILE_ERROR((ERROR_ARGS "Invalid retry"));
3898  }
3899  break;
3900  }
3901  case NODE_BEGIN:{
3902  COMPILE_(ret, "NODE_BEGIN", node->nd_body, poped);
3903  break;
3904  }
3905  case NODE_RESCUE:{
3906  LABEL *lstart = NEW_LABEL(line);
3907  LABEL *lend = NEW_LABEL(line);
3908  LABEL *lcont = NEW_LABEL(line);
3909  VALUE rescue = NEW_CHILD_ISEQVAL(
3910  node->nd_resq,
3911  rb_str_concat(rb_str_new2("rescue in "), iseq->location.label),
3912  ISEQ_TYPE_RESCUE, line);
3913 
3914  ADD_LABEL(ret, lstart);
3915  COMPILE(ret, "rescue head", node->nd_head);
3916  ADD_LABEL(ret, lend);
3917  if (node->nd_else) {
3918  ADD_INSN(ret, line, pop);
3919  COMPILE(ret, "rescue else", node->nd_else);
3920  }
3921  ADD_INSN(ret, line, nop);
3922  ADD_LABEL(ret, lcont);
3923 
3924  if (poped) {
3925  ADD_INSN(ret, line, pop);
3926  }
3927 
3928  /* register catch entry */
3929  ADD_CATCH_ENTRY(CATCH_TYPE_RESCUE, lstart, lend, rescue, lcont);
3930  ADD_CATCH_ENTRY(CATCH_TYPE_RETRY, lend, lcont, 0, lstart);
3931  break;
3932  }
3933  case NODE_RESBODY:{
3934  NODE *resq = node;
3935  NODE *narg;
3936  LABEL *label_miss, *label_hit;
3937 
3938  while (resq) {
3939  label_miss = NEW_LABEL(line);
3940  label_hit = NEW_LABEL(line);
3941 
3942  narg = resq->nd_args;
3943  if (narg) {
3944  switch (nd_type(narg)) {
3945  case NODE_ARRAY:
3946  while (narg) {
3947  ADD_INSN2(ret, line, getlocal, INT2FIX(2), INT2FIX(0));
3948  COMPILE(ret, "rescue arg", narg->nd_head);
3949  ADD_INSN1(ret, line, checkmatch, INT2FIX(VM_CHECKMATCH_TYPE_RESCUE));
3950  ADD_INSNL(ret, line, branchif, label_hit);
3951  narg = narg->nd_next;
3952  }
3953  break;
3954  case NODE_SPLAT:
3955  case NODE_ARGSCAT:
3956  case NODE_ARGSPUSH:
3957  ADD_INSN2(ret, line, getlocal, INT2FIX(2), INT2FIX(0));
3958  COMPILE(ret, "rescue/cond splat", narg);
3959  ADD_INSN1(ret, line, checkmatch, INT2FIX(VM_CHECKMATCH_TYPE_RESCUE | VM_CHECKMATCH_ARRAY));
3960  ADD_INSNL(ret, line, branchif, label_hit);
3961  break;
3962  default:
3963  rb_bug("NODE_RESBODY: unknown node (%s)",
3964  ruby_node_name(nd_type(narg)));
3965  }
3966  }
3967  else {
3968  ADD_INSN2(ret, line, getlocal, INT2FIX(2), INT2FIX(0));
3969  ADD_INSN1(ret, line, putobject, rb_eStandardError);
3970  ADD_INSN1(ret, line, checkmatch, INT2FIX(VM_CHECKMATCH_TYPE_RESCUE));
3971  ADD_INSNL(ret, line, branchif, label_hit);
3972  }
3973  ADD_INSNL(ret, line, jump, label_miss);
3974  ADD_LABEL(ret, label_hit);
3975  COMPILE(ret, "resbody body", resq->nd_body);
3976  if (iseq->compile_data->option->tailcall_optimization) {
3977  ADD_INSN(ret, line, nop);
3978  }
3979  ADD_INSN(ret, line, leave);
3980  ADD_LABEL(ret, label_miss);
3981  resq = resq->nd_head;
3982  }
3983  break;
3984  }
3985  case NODE_ENSURE:{
3986  DECL_ANCHOR(ensr);
3987  VALUE ensure = NEW_CHILD_ISEQVAL(node->nd_ensr,
3988  rb_str_concat(rb_str_new2
3989  ("ensure in "),
3990  iseq->location.label),
3991  ISEQ_TYPE_ENSURE, line);
3992  LABEL *lstart = NEW_LABEL(line);
3993  LABEL *lend = NEW_LABEL(line);
3994  LABEL *lcont = NEW_LABEL(line);
3995  struct ensure_range er;
3996  struct iseq_compile_data_ensure_node_stack enl;
3997  struct ensure_range *erange;
3998 
3999  INIT_ANCHOR(ensr);
4000  COMPILE_POPED(ensr, "ensure ensr", node->nd_ensr);
4001 
4002  er.begin = lstart;
4003  er.end = lend;
4004  er.next = 0;
4005  push_ensure_entry(iseq, &enl, &er, node->nd_ensr);
4006 
4007  ADD_LABEL(ret, lstart);
4008  COMPILE_(ret, "ensure head", node->nd_head, poped);
4009  ADD_LABEL(ret, lend);
4010  if (ensr->anchor.next == 0) {
4011  ADD_INSN(ret, line, nop);
4012  }
4013  else {
4014  ADD_SEQ(ret, ensr);
4015  }
4016  ADD_LABEL(ret, lcont);
4017 
4018  erange = iseq->compile_data->ensure_node_stack->erange;
4019  while (erange) {
4020  ADD_CATCH_ENTRY(CATCH_TYPE_ENSURE, erange->begin, erange->end,
4021  ensure, lcont);
4022  erange = erange->next;
4023  }
4024 
4025  iseq->compile_data->ensure_node_stack = enl.prev;
4026  break;
4027  }
4028 
4029  case NODE_AND:
4030  case NODE_OR:{
4031  LABEL *end_label = NEW_LABEL(line);
4032  COMPILE(ret, "nd_1st", node->nd_1st);
4033  if (!poped) {
4034  ADD_INSN(ret, line, dup);
4035  }
4036  if (type == NODE_AND) {
4037  ADD_INSNL(ret, line, branchunless, end_label);
4038  }
4039  else {
4040  ADD_INSNL(ret, line, branchif, end_label);
4041  }
4042  if (!poped) {
4043  ADD_INSN(ret, line, pop);
4044  }
4045  COMPILE_(ret, "nd_2nd", node->nd_2nd, poped);
4046  ADD_LABEL(ret, end_label);
4047  break;
4048  }
4049 
4050  case NODE_MASGN:{
4051  compile_massign(iseq, ret, node, poped);
4052  break;
4053  }
4054 
4055  case NODE_LASGN:{
4056  ID id = node->nd_vid;
4057  int idx = iseq->local_iseq->local_size - get_local_var_idx(iseq, id);
4058 
4059  debugs("lvar: %"PRIsVALUE" idx: %d\n", rb_id2str(id), idx);
4060  COMPILE(ret, "rvalue", node->nd_value);
4061 
4062  if (!poped) {
4063  ADD_INSN(ret, line, dup);
4064  }
4065  ADD_INSN2(ret, line, setlocal, INT2FIX(idx), INT2FIX(get_lvar_level(iseq)));
4066 
4067  break;
4068  }
4069  case NODE_DASGN:
4070  case NODE_DASGN_CURR:{
4071  int idx, lv, ls;
4072  COMPILE(ret, "dvalue", node->nd_value);
4073  debugi("dassn id", rb_id2str(node->nd_vid) ? node->nd_vid : '*');
4074 
4075  if (!poped) {
4076  ADD_INSN(ret, line, dup);
4077  }
4078 
4079  idx = get_dyna_var_idx(iseq, node->nd_vid, &lv, &ls);
4080 
4081  if (idx < 0) {
4082  rb_bug("NODE_DASGN(_CURR): unknown id (%"PRIsVALUE")", rb_id2str(node->nd_vid));
4083  }
4084 
4085  ADD_INSN2(ret, line, setlocal, INT2FIX(ls - idx), INT2FIX(lv));
4086  break;
4087  }
4088  case NODE_GASGN:{
4089  COMPILE(ret, "lvalue", node->nd_value);
4090 
4091  if (!poped) {
4092  ADD_INSN(ret, line, dup);
4093  }
4094  ADD_INSN1(ret, line, setglobal,
4095  ((VALUE)node->nd_entry | 1));
4096  break;
4097  }
4098  case NODE_IASGN:
4099  case NODE_IASGN2:{
4100  COMPILE(ret, "lvalue", node->nd_value);
4101  if (!poped) {
4102  ADD_INSN(ret, line, dup);
4103  }
4104  ADD_INSN2(ret, line, setinstancevariable,
4105  ID2SYM(node->nd_vid), INT2FIX(iseq->is_size++));
4106  break;
4107  }
4108  case NODE_CDECL:{
4109  COMPILE(ret, "lvalue", node->nd_value);
4110 
4111  if (!poped) {
4112  ADD_INSN(ret, line, dup);
4113  }
4114 
4115  if (node->nd_vid) {
4116  ADD_INSN1(ret, line, putspecialobject,
4117  INT2FIX(VM_SPECIAL_OBJECT_CONST_BASE));
4118  ADD_INSN1(ret, line, setconstant, ID2SYM(node->nd_vid));
4119  }
4120  else {
4121  compile_cpath(ret, iseq, node->nd_else);
4122  ADD_INSN1(ret, line, setconstant, ID2SYM(node->nd_else->nd_mid));
4123  }
4124  break;
4125  }
4126  case NODE_CVASGN:{
4127  COMPILE(ret, "cvasgn val", node->nd_value);
4128  if (!poped) {
4129  ADD_INSN(ret, line, dup);
4130  }
4131  ADD_INSN1(ret, line, setclassvariable,
4132  ID2SYM(node->nd_vid));
4133  break;
4134  }
4135  case NODE_OP_ASGN1: {
4136  DECL_ANCHOR(args);
4137  VALUE argc;
4138  unsigned int flag = 0;
4139  unsigned int asgnflag = 0;
4140  ID id = node->nd_mid;
4141  int boff = 0;
4142 
4143  /*
4144  * a[x] (op)= y
4145  *
4146  * nil # nil
4147  * eval a # nil a
4148  * eval x # nil a x
4149  * dupn 2 # nil a x a x
4150  * send :[] # nil a x a[x]
4151  * eval y # nil a x a[x] y
4152  * send op # nil a x ret
4153  * setn 3 # ret a x ret
4154  * send []= # ret ?
4155  * pop # ret
4156  */
4157 
4158  /*
4159  * nd_recv[nd_args->nd_body] (nd_mid)= nd_args->nd_head;
4160  * NODE_OP_ASGN nd_recv
4161  * nd_args->nd_head
4162  * nd_args->nd_body
4163  * nd_mid
4164  */
4165 
4166  if (!poped) {
4167  ADD_INSN(ret, line, putnil);
4168  }
4169  asgnflag = COMPILE_RECV(ret, "NODE_OP_ASGN1 recv", node);
4170  switch (nd_type(node->nd_args->nd_head)) {
4171  case NODE_ZARRAY:
4172  argc = INT2FIX(0);
4173  break;
4174  case NODE_BLOCK_PASS:
4175  boff = 1;
4176  default:
4177  INIT_ANCHOR(args);
4178  argc = setup_args(iseq, args, node->nd_args->nd_head, &flag, NULL);
4179  ADD_SEQ(ret, args);
4180  }
4181  ADD_INSN1(ret, line, dupn, FIXNUM_INC(argc, 1 + boff));
4182  ADD_SEND_WITH_FLAG(ret, line, idAREF, argc, INT2FIX(flag));
4183  flag |= asgnflag;
4184 
4185  if (id == 0 || id == 1) {
4186  /* 0: or, 1: and
4187  a[x] ||= y
4188 
4189  unless/if a[x]
4190  a[x]= y
4191  else
4192  nil
4193  end
4194  */
4195  LABEL *label = NEW_LABEL(line);
4196  LABEL *lfin = NEW_LABEL(line);
4197 
4198  ADD_INSN(ret, line, dup);
4199  if (id == 0) {
4200  /* or */
4201  ADD_INSNL(ret, line, branchif, label);
4202  }
4203  else {
4204  /* and */
4205  ADD_INSNL(ret, line, branchunless, label);
4206  }
4207  ADD_INSN(ret, line, pop);
4208 
4209  COMPILE(ret, "NODE_OP_ASGN1 args->body: ", node->nd_args->nd_body);
4210  if (!poped) {
4211  ADD_INSN1(ret, line, setn, FIXNUM_INC(argc, 2+boff));
4212  }
4213  if (flag & VM_CALL_ARGS_SPLAT) {
4214  ADD_INSN1(ret, line, newarray, INT2FIX(1));
4215  if (boff > 0) {
4216  ADD_INSN1(ret, line, dupn, INT2FIX(3));
4217  ADD_INSN(ret, line, swap);
4218  ADD_INSN(ret, line, pop);
4219  }
4220  ADD_INSN(ret, line, concatarray);
4221  if (boff > 0) {
4222  ADD_INSN1(ret, line, setn, INT2FIX(3));
4223  ADD_INSN(ret, line, pop);
4224  ADD_INSN(ret, line, pop);
4225  }
4226  ADD_SEND_WITH_FLAG(ret, line, idASET, argc, INT2FIX(flag));
4227  }
4228  else {
4229  if (boff > 0)
4230  ADD_INSN(ret, line, swap);
4231  ADD_SEND_WITH_FLAG(ret, line, idASET, FIXNUM_INC(argc, 1), INT2FIX(flag));
4232  }
4233  ADD_INSN(ret, line, pop);
4234  ADD_INSNL(ret, line, jump, lfin);
4235  ADD_LABEL(ret, label);
4236  if (!poped) {
4237  ADD_INSN1(ret, line, setn, FIXNUM_INC(argc, 2+boff));
4238  }
4239  ADD_INSN1(ret, line, adjuststack, FIXNUM_INC(argc, 2+boff));
4240  ADD_LABEL(ret, lfin);
4241  }
4242  else {
4243  COMPILE(ret, "NODE_OP_ASGN1 args->body: ", node->nd_args->nd_body);
4244  ADD_SEND(ret, line, id, INT2FIX(1));
4245  if (!poped) {
4246  ADD_INSN1(ret, line, setn, FIXNUM_INC(argc, 2+boff));
4247  }
4248  if (flag & VM_CALL_ARGS_SPLAT) {
4249  ADD_INSN1(ret, line, newarray, INT2FIX(1));
4250  if (boff > 0) {
4251  ADD_INSN1(ret, line, dupn, INT2FIX(3));
4252  ADD_INSN(ret, line, swap);
4253  ADD_INSN(ret, line, pop);
4254  }
4255  ADD_INSN(ret, line, concatarray);
4256  if (boff > 0) {
4257  ADD_INSN1(ret, line, setn, INT2FIX(3));
4258  ADD_INSN(ret, line, pop);
4259  ADD_INSN(ret, line, pop);
4260  }
4261  ADD_SEND_WITH_FLAG(ret, line, idASET, argc, INT2FIX(flag));
4262  }
4263  else {
4264  if (boff > 0)
4265  ADD_INSN(ret, line, swap);
4266  ADD_SEND_WITH_FLAG(ret, line, idASET, FIXNUM_INC(argc, 1), INT2FIX(flag));
4267  }
4268  ADD_INSN(ret, line, pop);
4269  }
4270 
4271  break;
4272  }
4273  case NODE_OP_ASGN2:{
4274  ID atype = node->nd_next->nd_mid;
4275  VALUE asgnflag;
4276  LABEL *lfin = NEW_LABEL(line);
4277  LABEL *lcfin = NEW_LABEL(line);
4278  /*
4279  class C; attr_accessor :c; end
4280  r = C.new
4281  r.a &&= v # asgn2
4282 
4283  eval r # r
4284  dup # r r
4285  eval r.a # r o
4286 
4287  # or
4288  dup # r o o
4289  if lcfin # r o
4290  pop # r
4291  eval v # r v
4292  swap # v r
4293  topn 1 # v r v
4294  send a= # v ?
4295  jump lfin # v ?
4296 
4297  lcfin: # r o
4298  swap # o r
4299 
4300  lfin: # o ?
4301  pop # o
4302 
4303  # and
4304  dup # r o o
4305  unless lcfin
4306  pop # r
4307  eval v # r v
4308  swap # v r
4309  topn 1 # v r v
4310  send a= # v ?
4311  jump lfin # v ?
4312 
4313  # others
4314  eval v # r o v
4315  send ?? # r w
4316  send a= # w
4317 
4318  */
4319 
4320  asgnflag = COMPILE_RECV(ret, "NODE_OP_ASGN2#recv", node);
4321  ADD_INSN(ret, line, dup);
4322  ADD_SEND(ret, line, node->nd_next->nd_vid, INT2FIX(0));
4323 
4324  if (atype == 0 || atype == 1) { /* 0: OR or 1: AND */
4325  ADD_INSN(ret, line, dup);
4326  if (atype == 0) {
4327  ADD_INSNL(ret, line, branchif, lcfin);
4328  }
4329  else {
4330  ADD_INSNL(ret, line, branchunless, lcfin);
4331  }
4332  ADD_INSN(ret, line, pop);
4333  COMPILE(ret, "NODE_OP_ASGN2 val", node->nd_value);
4334  ADD_INSN(ret, line, swap);
4335  ADD_INSN1(ret, line, topn, INT2FIX(1));
4336  ADD_SEND_WITH_FLAG(ret, line, node->nd_next->nd_aid, INT2FIX(1), INT2FIX(asgnflag));
4337  ADD_INSNL(ret, line, jump, lfin);
4338 
4339  ADD_LABEL(ret, lcfin);
4340  ADD_INSN(ret, line, swap);
4341 
4342  ADD_LABEL(ret, lfin);
4343  ADD_INSN(ret, line, pop);
4344  if (poped) {
4345  /* we can apply more optimize */
4346  ADD_INSN(ret, line, pop);
4347  }
4348  }
4349  else {
4350  COMPILE(ret, "NODE_OP_ASGN2 val", node->nd_value);
4351  ADD_SEND(ret, line, node->nd_next->nd_mid,
4352  INT2FIX(1));
4353  if (!poped) {
4354  ADD_INSN(ret, line, swap);
4355  ADD_INSN1(ret, line, topn, INT2FIX(1));
4356  }
4357  ADD_SEND_WITH_FLAG(ret, line, node->nd_next->nd_aid, INT2FIX(1), INT2FIX(asgnflag));
4358  ADD_INSN(ret, line, pop);
4359  }
4360  break;
4361  }
4362  case NODE_OP_CDECL: {
4363  LABEL *lfin = 0;
4364  LABEL *lassign = 0;
4365  ID mid;
4366 
4367  switch (nd_type(node->nd_head)) {
4368  case NODE_COLON3:
4369  ADD_INSN1(ret, line, putobject, rb_cObject);
4370  break;
4371  case NODE_COLON2:
4372  COMPILE(ret, "NODE_OP_CDECL/colon2#nd_head", node->nd_head->nd_head);
4373  break;
4374  default:
4375  do {
4376  COMPILE_ERROR((ERROR_ARGS "%s: invalid node in NODE_OP_CDECL",
4377  ruby_node_name(nd_type(node->nd_head))));
4378  } while (0);
4379  return COMPILE_NG;
4380  }
4381  mid = node->nd_head->nd_mid;
4382  /* cref */
4383  if (node->nd_aid == 0) {
4384  lassign = NEW_LABEL(line);
4385  ADD_INSN(ret, line, dup); /* cref cref */
4386  ADD_INSN3(ret, line, defined, INT2FIX(DEFINED_CONST),
4387  ID2SYM(mid), Qfalse); /* cref bool */
4388  ADD_INSNL(ret, line, branchunless, lassign); /* cref */
4389  }
4390  ADD_INSN(ret, line, dup); /* cref cref */
4391  ADD_INSN1(ret, line, getconstant, ID2SYM(mid)); /* cref obj */
4392 
4393  if (node->nd_aid == 0 || node->nd_aid == 1) {
4394  lfin = NEW_LABEL(line);
4395  if (!poped) ADD_INSN(ret, line, dup); /* cref [obj] obj */
4396  if (node->nd_aid == 0)
4397  ADD_INSNL(ret, line, branchif, lfin);
4398  else
4399  ADD_INSNL(ret, line, branchunless, lfin);
4400  /* cref [obj] */
4401  if (!poped) ADD_INSN(ret, line, pop); /* cref */
4402  if (lassign) ADD_LABEL(ret, lassign);
4403  COMPILE(ret, "NODE_OP_CDECL#nd_value", node->nd_value);
4404  /* cref value */
4405  if (poped)
4406  ADD_INSN1(ret, line, topn, INT2FIX(1)); /* cref value cref */
4407  else {
4408  ADD_INSN1(ret, line, dupn, INT2FIX(2)); /* cref value cref value */
4409  ADD_INSN(ret, line, swap); /* cref value value cref */
4410  }
4411  ADD_INSN1(ret, line, setconstant, ID2SYM(mid)); /* cref [value] */
4412  ADD_LABEL(ret, lfin); /* cref [value] */
4413  if (!poped) ADD_INSN(ret, line, swap); /* [value] cref */
4414  ADD_INSN(ret, line, pop); /* [value] */
4415  }
4416  else {
4417  COMPILE(ret, "NODE_OP_CDECL#nd_value", node->nd_value);
4418  /* cref obj value */
4419  ADD_CALL(ret, line, node->nd_aid, INT2FIX(1));
4420  /* cref value */
4421  ADD_INSN(ret, line, swap); /* value cref */
4422  if (!poped) {
4423  ADD_INSN1(ret, line, topn, INT2FIX(1)); /* value cref value */
4424  ADD_INSN(ret, line, swap); /* value value cref */
4425  }
4426  ADD_INSN1(ret, line, setconstant, ID2SYM(mid));
4427  }
4428  break;
4429  }
4430  case NODE_OP_ASGN_AND:
4431  case NODE_OP_ASGN_OR:{
4432  LABEL *lfin = NEW_LABEL(line);
4433  LABEL *lassign;
4434 
4435  if (nd_type(node) == NODE_OP_ASGN_OR) {
4436  LABEL *lfinish[2];
4437  lfinish[0] = lfin;
4438  lfinish[1] = 0;
4439  defined_expr(iseq, ret, node->nd_head, lfinish, Qfalse);
4440  lassign = lfinish[1];
4441  if (!lassign) {
4442  lassign = NEW_LABEL(line);
4443  }
4444  ADD_INSNL(ret, line, branchunless, lassign);
4445  }
4446  else {
4447  lassign = NEW_LABEL(line);
4448  }
4449 
4450  COMPILE(ret, "NODE_OP_ASGN_AND/OR#nd_head", node->nd_head);
4451  ADD_INSN(ret, line, dup);
4452 
4453  if (nd_type(node) == NODE_OP_ASGN_AND) {
4454  ADD_INSNL(ret, line, branchunless, lfin);
4455  }
4456  else {
4457  ADD_INSNL(ret, line, branchif, lfin);
4458  }
4459 
4460  ADD_INSN(ret, line, pop);
4461  ADD_LABEL(ret, lassign);
4462  COMPILE(ret, "NODE_OP_ASGN_AND/OR#nd_value", node->nd_value);
4463  ADD_LABEL(ret, lfin);
4464 
4465  if (poped) {
4466  /* we can apply more optimize */
4467  ADD_INSN(ret, line, pop);
4468  }
4469  break;
4470  }
4471  case NODE_CALL:
4472  /* optimization shortcut
4473  * "literal".freeze -> opt_str_freeze("literal")
4474  */
4475  if (node->nd_recv && nd_type(node->nd_recv) == NODE_STR &&
4476  node->nd_mid == idFreeze && node->nd_args == NULL &&
4477  iseq->compile_data->current_block == Qfalse &&
4478  iseq->compile_data->option->specialized_instruction) {
4479  VALUE str = rb_fstring(node->nd_recv->nd_lit);
4480  iseq_add_mark_object(iseq, str);
4481  ADD_INSN1(ret, line, opt_str_freeze, str);
4482  if (poped) {
4483  ADD_INSN(ret, line, pop);
4484  }
4485  break;
4486  }
4487  /* optimization shortcut
4488  * obj["literal"] -> opt_aref_with(obj, "literal")
4489  */
4490  if (node->nd_mid == idAREF && !private_recv_p(node) && node->nd_args &&
4491  nd_type(node->nd_args) == NODE_ARRAY && node->nd_args->nd_alen == 1 &&
4492  nd_type(node->nd_args->nd_head) == NODE_STR &&
4493  iseq->compile_data->current_block == Qfalse &&
4494  iseq->compile_data->option->specialized_instruction) {
4495  VALUE str = rb_fstring(node->nd_args->nd_head->nd_lit);
4496  node->nd_args->nd_head->nd_lit = str;
4497  COMPILE(ret, "recv", node->nd_recv);
4498  ADD_INSN2(ret, line, opt_aref_with,
4499  new_callinfo(iseq, idAREF, 1, 0, 0, NULL), str);
4500  if (poped) {
4501  ADD_INSN(ret, line, pop);
4502  }
4503  break;
4504  }
4505  case NODE_FCALL:
4506  case NODE_VCALL:{ /* VCALL: variable or call */
4507  /*
4508  call: obj.method(...)
4509  fcall: func(...)
4510  vcall: func
4511  */
4512  DECL_ANCHOR(recv);
4513  DECL_ANCHOR(args);
4514  ID mid = node->nd_mid;
4515  VALUE argc;
4516  unsigned int flag = 0;
4517  rb_call_info_kw_arg_t *keywords = NULL;
4518  VALUE parent_block = iseq->compile_data->current_block;
4519  iseq->compile_data->current_block = Qfalse;
4520 
4521  INIT_ANCHOR(recv);
4522  INIT_ANCHOR(args);
4523 #if SUPPORT_JOKE
4524  if (nd_type(node) == NODE_VCALL) {
4525  ID id_bitblt;
4526  ID id_answer;
4527 
4528  CONST_ID(id_bitblt, "bitblt");
4529  CONST_ID(id_answer, "the_answer_to_life_the_universe_and_everything");
4530 
4531  if (mid == id_bitblt) {
4532  ADD_INSN(ret, line, bitblt);
4533  break;
4534  }
4535  else if (mid == id_answer) {
4536  ADD_INSN(ret, line, answer);
4537  break;
4538  }
4539  }
4540  /* only joke */
4541  {
4542  ID goto_id;
4543  ID label_id;
4544 
4545  CONST_ID(goto_id, "__goto__");
4546  CONST_ID(label_id, "__label__");
4547 
4548  if (nd_type(node) == NODE_FCALL &&
4549  (mid == goto_id || mid == label_id)) {
4550  LABEL *label;
4551  st_data_t data;
4552  st_table *labels_table = iseq->compile_data->labels_table;
4553  ID label_name;
4554 
4555  if (!labels_table) {
4556  labels_table = st_init_numtable();
4557  iseq->compile_data->labels_table = labels_table;
4558  }
4559  if (nd_type(node->nd_args->nd_head) == NODE_LIT &&
4560  SYMBOL_P(node->nd_args->nd_head->nd_lit)) {
4561 
4562  label_name = SYM2ID(node->nd_args->nd_head->nd_lit);
4563  if (!st_lookup(labels_table, (st_data_t)label_name, &data)) {
4564  label = NEW_LABEL(line);
4565  label->position = line;
4566  st_insert(labels_table, (st_data_t)label_name, (st_data_t)label);
4567  }
4568  else {
4569  label = (LABEL *)data;
4570  }
4571  }
4572  else {
4573  COMPILE_ERROR((ERROR_ARGS "invalid goto/label format"));
4574  }
4575 
4576 
4577  if (mid == goto_id) {
4578  ADD_INSNL(ret, line, jump, label);
4579  }
4580  else {
4581  ADD_LABEL(ret, label);
4582  }
4583  break;
4584  }
4585  }
4586 #endif
4587  /* receiver */
4588  if (type == NODE_CALL) {
4589  COMPILE(recv, "recv", node->nd_recv);
4590  }
4591  else if (type == NODE_FCALL || type == NODE_VCALL) {
4592  ADD_CALL_RECEIVER(recv, line);
4593  }
4594 
4595  /* args */
4596  if (nd_type(node) != NODE_VCALL) {
4597  argc = setup_args(iseq, args, node->nd_args, &flag, &keywords);
4598  }
4599  else {
4600  argc = INT2FIX(0);
4601  }
4602 
4603  ADD_SEQ(ret, recv);
4604  ADD_SEQ(ret, args);
4605 
4606  debugp_param("call args argc", argc);
4607  debugp_param("call method", ID2SYM(mid));
4608 
4609  switch (nd_type(node)) {
4610  case NODE_VCALL:
4611  flag |= VM_CALL_VCALL;
4612  /* VCALL is funcall, so fall through */
4613  case NODE_FCALL:
4614  flag |= VM_CALL_FCALL;
4615  }
4616 
4617  ADD_SEND_R(ret, line, mid, argc, parent_block, INT2FIX(flag), keywords);
4618 
4619  if (poped) {
4620  ADD_INSN(ret, line, pop);
4621  }
4622  break;
4623  }
4624  case NODE_SUPER:
4625  case NODE_ZSUPER:{
4626  DECL_ANCHOR(args);
4627  int argc;
4628  unsigned int flag = 0;
4629  rb_call_info_kw_arg_t *keywords = NULL;
4630  VALUE parent_block = iseq->compile_data->current_block;
4631 
4632  INIT_ANCHOR(args);
4633  iseq->compile_data->current_block = Qfalse;
4634  if (nd_type(node) == NODE_SUPER) {
4635  VALUE vargc = setup_args(iseq, args, node->nd_args, &flag, &keywords);
4636  argc = FIX2INT(vargc);
4637  }
4638  else {
4639  /* NODE_ZSUPER */
4640  int i;
4641  rb_iseq_t *liseq = iseq->local_iseq;
4642  int lvar_level = get_lvar_level(iseq);
4643 
4644  argc = liseq->param.lead_num;
4645 
4646  /* normal arguments */
4647  for (i = 0; i < liseq->param.lead_num; i++) {
4648  int idx = liseq->local_size - i;
4649  ADD_INSN2(args, line, getlocal, INT2FIX(idx), INT2FIX(lvar_level));
4650  }
4651 
4652  if (liseq->param.flags.has_opt) {
4653  /* optional arguments */
4654  int j;
4655  for (j = 0; j < liseq->param.opt_num; j++) {
4656  int idx = liseq->local_size - (i + j);
4657  ADD_INSN2(args, line, getlocal, INT2FIX(idx), INT2FIX(lvar_level));
4658  }
4659  i += j;
4660  argc = i;
4661  }
4662  if (liseq->param.flags.has_rest) {
4663  /* rest argument */
4664  int idx = liseq->local_size - liseq->param.rest_start;
4665  ADD_INSN2(args, line, getlocal, INT2FIX(idx), INT2FIX(lvar_level));
4666  argc = liseq->param.rest_start + 1;
4667  flag |= VM_CALL_ARGS_SPLAT;
4668  }
4669  if (liseq->param.flags.has_post) {
4670  /* post arguments */
4671  int post_len = liseq->param.post_num;
4672  int post_start = liseq->param.post_start;
4673 
4674  if (liseq->param.flags.has_rest) {
4675  int j;
4676  for (j=0; j<post_len; j++) {
4677  int idx = liseq->local_size - (post_start + j);
4678  ADD_INSN2(args, line, getlocal, INT2FIX(idx), INT2FIX(lvar_level));
4679  }
4680  ADD_INSN1(args, line, newarray, INT2FIX(j));
4681  ADD_INSN (args, line, concatarray);
4682  /* argc is settled at above */
4683  }
4684  else {
4685  int j;
4686  for (j=0; j<post_len; j++) {
4687  int idx = liseq->local_size - (post_start + j);
4688  ADD_INSN2(args, line, getlocal, INT2FIX(idx), INT2FIX(lvar_level));
4689  }
4690  argc = post_len + post_start;
4691  }
4692  }
4693 
4694  if (liseq->param.flags.has_kw) { /* TODO: support keywords */
4695  int local_size = liseq->local_size;
4696  argc++;
4697 
4698  ADD_INSN1(args, line, putspecialobject, INT2FIX(VM_SPECIAL_OBJECT_VMCORE));
4699 
4700  if (liseq->param.flags.has_kwrest) {
4701  ADD_INSN2(args, line, getlocal, INT2FIX(liseq->local_size - liseq->param.keyword->rest_start), INT2FIX(lvar_level));
4702  ADD_SEND (args, line, rb_intern("dup"), INT2FIX(0));
4703  }
4704  else {
4705  ADD_INSN1(args, line, newhash, INT2FIX(0));
4706  }
4707  for (i = 0; i < liseq->param.keyword->num; ++i) {
4708  ID id = liseq->param.keyword->table[i];
4709  int idx = local_size - get_local_var_idx(liseq, id);
4710  ADD_INSN1(args, line, putobject, ID2SYM(id));
4711  ADD_INSN2(args, line, getlocal, INT2FIX(idx), INT2FIX(lvar_level));
4712  }
4713  ADD_SEND(args, line, id_core_hash_merge_ptr, INT2FIX(i * 2 + 1));
4714  if (liseq->param.flags.has_rest) {
4715  ADD_INSN1(args, line, newarray, INT2FIX(1));
4716  ADD_INSN (args, line, concatarray);
4717  --argc;
4718  }
4719  }
4720  else if (liseq->param.flags.has_kwrest) {
4721  ADD_INSN2(args, line, getlocal, INT2FIX(liseq->local_size - liseq->param.keyword->rest_start), INT2FIX(lvar_level));
4722  ADD_SEND (args, line, rb_intern("dup"), INT2FIX(0));
4723  if (liseq->param.flags.has_rest) {
4724  ADD_INSN1(args, line, newarray, INT2FIX(1));
4725  ADD_INSN (args, line, concatarray);
4726  }
4727  else {
4728  argc++;
4729  }
4730  }
4731  }
4732 
4733  /* dummy receiver */
4734  ADD_INSN1(ret, line, putobject, nd_type(node) == NODE_ZSUPER ? Qfalse : Qtrue);
4735  ADD_SEQ(ret, args);
4736  ADD_INSN1(ret, line, invokesuper, new_callinfo(iseq, 0, argc, parent_block,
4737  flag | VM_CALL_SUPER | VM_CALL_FCALL, keywords));
4738 
4739  if (poped) {
4740  ADD_INSN(ret, line, pop);
4741  }
4742  break;
4743  }
4744  case NODE_ARRAY:{
4745  compile_array_(iseq, ret, node, COMPILE_ARRAY_TYPE_ARRAY, NULL, poped);
4746  break;
4747  }
4748  case NODE_ZARRAY:{
4749  if (!poped) {
4750  ADD_INSN1(ret, line, newarray, INT2FIX(0));
4751  }
4752  break;
4753  }
4754  case NODE_VALUES:{
4755  NODE *n = node;
4756  while (n) {
4757  COMPILE(ret, "values item", n->nd_head);
4758  n = n->nd_next;
4759  }
4760  ADD_INSN1(ret, line, newarray, INT2FIX(node->nd_alen));
4761  if (poped) {
4762  ADD_INSN(ret, line, pop);
4763  }
4764  break;
4765  }
4766  case NODE_HASH:{
4767  DECL_ANCHOR(list);
4768  int type = node->nd_head ? nd_type(node->nd_head) : NODE_ZARRAY;
4769 
4770  INIT_ANCHOR(list);
4771  switch (type) {
4772  case NODE_ARRAY:
4773  compile_array(iseq, list, node->nd_head, COMPILE_ARRAY_TYPE_HASH);
4774  ADD_SEQ(ret, list);
4775  break;
4776 
4777  case NODE_ZARRAY:
4778  ADD_INSN1(ret, line, newhash, INT2FIX(0));
4779  break;
4780 
4781  default:
4782  rb_bug("can't make hash with this node: %s", ruby_node_name(type));
4783  }
4784 
4785  if (poped) {
4786  ADD_INSN(ret, line, pop);
4787  }
4788  break;
4789  }
4790  case NODE_RETURN:{
4791  rb_iseq_t *is = iseq;
4792 
4793  if (is) {
4794  if (is->type == ISEQ_TYPE_TOP) {
4795  COMPILE_ERROR((ERROR_ARGS "Invalid return"));
4796  }
4797  else {
4798  LABEL *splabel = 0;
4799 
4800  if (is->type == ISEQ_TYPE_METHOD) {
4801  splabel = NEW_LABEL(0);
4802  ADD_LABEL(ret, splabel);
4803  ADD_ADJUST(ret, line, 0);
4804  }
4805 
4806  COMPILE(ret, "return nd_stts (return val)", node->nd_stts);
4807 
4808  if (is->type == ISEQ_TYPE_METHOD) {
4809  add_ensure_iseq(ret, iseq, 1);
4810  ADD_TRACE(ret, line, RUBY_EVENT_RETURN);
4811  ADD_INSN(ret, line, leave);
4812  ADD_ADJUST_RESTORE(ret, splabel);
4813 
4814  if (!poped) {
4815  ADD_INSN(ret, line, putnil);
4816  }
4817  }
4818  else {
4819  ADD_INSN1(ret, line, throw, INT2FIX(0x01) /* TAG_RETURN */ );
4820  if (poped) {
4821  ADD_INSN(ret, line, pop);
4822  }
4823  }
4824  }
4825  }
4826  break;
4827  }
4828  case NODE_YIELD:{
4829  DECL_ANCHOR(args);
4830  VALUE argc;
4831  unsigned int flag = 0;
4832  rb_call_info_kw_arg_t *keywords = NULL;
4833 
4834  INIT_ANCHOR(args);
4835  if (iseq->type == ISEQ_TYPE_TOP) {
4836  COMPILE_ERROR((ERROR_ARGS "Invalid yield"));
4837  }
4838 
4839  if (node->nd_head) {
4840  argc = setup_args(iseq, args, node->nd_head, &flag, &keywords);
4841  }
4842  else {
4843  argc = INT2FIX(0);
4844  }
4845 
4846  ADD_SEQ(ret, args);
4847  ADD_INSN1(ret, line, invokeblock, new_callinfo(iseq, 0, FIX2INT(argc), 0, flag, keywords));
4848 
4849  if (poped) {
4850  ADD_INSN(ret, line, pop);
4851  }
4852  break;
4853  }
4854  case NODE_LVAR:{
4855  if (!poped) {
4856  ID id = node->nd_vid;
4857  int idx = iseq->local_iseq->local_size - get_local_var_idx(iseq, id);
4858 
4859  debugs("id: %"PRIsVALUE" idx: %d\n", rb_id2str(id), idx);
4860  ADD_INSN2(ret, line, getlocal, INT2FIX(idx), INT2FIX(get_lvar_level(iseq)));
4861  }
4862  break;
4863  }
4864  case NODE_DVAR:{
4865  int lv, idx, ls;
4866  debugi("nd_vid", node->nd_vid);
4867  if (!poped) {
4868  idx = get_dyna_var_idx(iseq, node->nd_vid, &lv, &ls);
4869  if (idx < 0) {
4870  rb_bug("unknown dvar (%"PRIsVALUE")", rb_id2str(node->nd_vid));
4871  }
4872  ADD_INSN2(ret, line, getlocal, INT2FIX(ls - idx), INT2FIX(lv));
4873  }
4874  break;
4875  }
4876  case NODE_GVAR:{
4877  ADD_INSN1(ret, line, getglobal,
4878  ((VALUE)node->nd_entry | 1));
4879  if (poped) {
4880  ADD_INSN(ret, line, pop);
4881  }
4882  break;
4883  }
4884  case NODE_IVAR:{
4885  debugi("nd_vid", node->nd_vid);
4886  if (!poped) {
4887  ADD_INSN2(ret, line, getinstancevariable,
4888  ID2SYM(node->nd_vid), INT2FIX(iseq->is_size++));
4889  }
4890  break;
4891  }
4892  case NODE_CONST:{
4893  debugi("nd_vid", node->nd_vid);
4894 
4895  if (iseq->compile_data->option->inline_const_cache) {
4896  LABEL *lend = NEW_LABEL(line);
4897  int ic_index = iseq->is_size++;
4898 
4899  ADD_INSN2(ret, line, getinlinecache, lend, INT2FIX(ic_index));
4900  ADD_INSN1(ret, line, getconstant, ID2SYM(node->nd_vid));
4901  ADD_INSN1(ret, line, setinlinecache, INT2FIX(ic_index));
4902  ADD_LABEL(ret, lend);
4903  }
4904  else {
4905  ADD_INSN(ret, line, putnil);
4906  ADD_INSN1(ret, line, getconstant, ID2SYM(node->nd_vid));
4907  }
4908 
4909  if (poped) {
4910  ADD_INSN(ret, line, pop);
4911  }
4912  break;
4913  }
4914  case NODE_CVAR:{
4915  if (!poped) {
4916  ADD_INSN1(ret, line, getclassvariable,
4917  ID2SYM(node->nd_vid));
4918  }
4919  break;
4920  }
4921  case NODE_NTH_REF:{
4922  if (!poped) {
4923  if (!node->nd_nth) {
4924  ADD_INSN(ret, line, putnil);
4925  break;
4926  }

4928  INT2FIX(node->nd_nth << 1));
4929  }
4930  break;
4931  }

4933  if (!poped) {
4934  ADD_INSN2(ret, line, getspecial, INT2FIX(1) /* '~' */,
4935  INT2FIX(0x01 | (node->nd_nth << 1)));
4936  }
4937  break;
4938  }
4939  case NODE_MATCH:
4940  case NODE_MATCH2:
4941  case NODE_MATCH3:{
4942  DECL_ANCHOR(recv);
4943  DECL_ANCHOR(val);
4944 
4945  INIT_ANCHOR(recv);
4946  INIT_ANCHOR(val);
4947  switch (nd_type(node)) {
4948  case NODE_MATCH:
4949  ADD_INSN1(recv, line, putobject, node->nd_lit);

4951  INT2FIX(0));
4952  break;
4953  case NODE_MATCH2:
4954  COMPILE(recv, "receiver", node->nd_recv);
4955  COMPILE(val, "value", node->nd_value);
4956  break;
4957  case NODE_MATCH3:
4958  COMPILE(recv, "receiver", node->nd_value);
4959  COMPILE(val, "value", node->nd_recv);
4960  break;
4961  }
4962

4966  INSN_OF(recv->last) == BIN(putobject) &&

4968  ADD_SEQ(ret, val);
4969  ADD_INSN1(ret, line, opt_regexpmatch1,

4971  }

4973  ADD_SEQ(ret, recv);
4974  ADD_SEQ(ret, val);
4975  ADD_INSN1(ret, line, opt_regexpmatch2, new_callinfo(iseq, idEqTilde, 1, 0, 0, NULL));
4976  }
4977  }
4978  else {
4979  ADD_SEQ(ret, recv);
4980  ADD_SEQ(ret, val);
4981  ADD_SEND(ret, line, idEqTilde, INT2FIX(1));
4982  }
4983

4985  ADD_INSN(ret, line, pop);
4986  }
4987  break;
4988  }
4989  case NODE_LIT:{
4990  debugp_param("lit", node->nd_lit);
4991  if (!poped) {
4992  ADD_INSN1(ret, line, putobject, node->nd_lit);
4993  }
4994  break;
4995  }
4996  case NODE_STR:{
4997  node->nd_lit = rb_fstring(node->nd_lit);
4998  debugp_param("nd_lit", node->nd_lit);
4999  if (!poped) {
5000  ADD_INSN1(ret, line, putstring, node->nd_lit);
5001  }

5003  }

5353  }

5440  case NODE_KW_ARG:
5441  {
5442  LABEL *end_label = NEW_LABEL(nd_line(node));
5443  NODE *default_value = node->nd_body->nd_value;
5444 
5445  if (default_value == (NODE *)-1) {
5446  /* required argument. do nothing */
5447  rb_bug("unreachable");

5449  else if (nd_type(default_value) == NODE_LIT ||
5450  nd_type(default_value) == NODE_NIL ||
5451  nd_type(default_value) == NODE_TRUE ||
5452  nd_type(default_value) == NODE_FALSE) {
5453  rb_bug("unreachable");
5454  }

5457  * kw = default_value
5458  * end

5460  int kw_bits_idx = iseq->local_size - iseq->param.keyword->bits_start;
5461  int keyword_idx = iseq->param.keyword->num;
5462 
5463  ADD_INSN2(ret, line, checkkeyword, INT2FIX(kw_bits_idx), INT2FIX(keyword_idx));
5464  ADD_INSNL(ret, line, branchif, end_label);

5480  }
5481  case NODE_ATTRASGN:{
5482  DECL_ANCHOR(recv);
5483  DECL_ANCHOR(args);
5484  unsigned int flag = 0;
5485  VALUE argc;
5486 
5487  /* optimization shortcut
5488  * obj["literal"] = value -> opt_aset_with(obj, "literal", value)
5489  */
5490  if (node->nd_mid == idASET && !private_recv_p(node) && node->nd_args &&
5491  nd_type(node->nd_args) == NODE_ARRAY && node->nd_args->nd_alen == 2 &&
5492  nd_type(node->nd_args->nd_head) == NODE_STR &&
5493  iseq->compile_data->current_block == Qfalse &&
5494  iseq->compile_data->option->specialized_instruction)
5495  {
5496  VALUE str = rb_fstring(node->nd_args->nd_head->nd_lit);
5497  node->nd_args->nd_head->nd_lit = str;
5498  iseq_add_mark_object(iseq, str);
5499  COMPILE(ret, "recv", node->nd_recv);
5500  COMPILE(ret, "value", node->nd_args->nd_next->nd_head);
5501  if (!poped) {
5502  ADD_INSN(ret, line, swap);
5503  ADD_INSN1(ret, line, topn, INT2FIX(1));
5504  }
5505  ADD_INSN2(ret, line, opt_aset_with,
5506  new_callinfo(iseq, idASET, 2, 0, 0, NULL), str);
5507  ADD_INSN(ret, line, pop);
5508  break;
5509  }
5510 
5511  INIT_ANCHOR(recv);
5512  INIT_ANCHOR(args);
5513  argc = setup_args(iseq, args, node->nd_args, &flag, NULL);
5514 
5515  flag |= COMPILE_RECV(recv, "recv", node);
5516 
5517  debugp_param("argc", argc);
5518  debugp_param("nd_mid", ID2SYM(node->nd_mid));
5519 
5520  if (!poped) {
5521  ADD_INSN(ret, line, putnil);
5522  ADD_SEQ(ret, recv);
5523  ADD_SEQ(ret, args);
5524 
5525  if (flag & VM_CALL_ARGS_BLOCKARG) {
5526  ADD_INSN1(ret, line, topn, INT2FIX(1));
5527  if (flag & VM_CALL_ARGS_SPLAT) {
5528  ADD_INSN1(ret, line, putobject, INT2FIX(-1));
5529  ADD_SEND(ret, line, idAREF, INT2FIX(1));
5530  }
5531  ADD_INSN1(ret, line, setn, FIXNUM_INC(argc, 3));
5532  ADD_INSN (ret, line, pop);
5533  }
5534  else if (flag & VM_CALL_ARGS_SPLAT) {
5535  ADD_INSN(ret, line, dup);
5536  ADD_INSN1(ret, line, putobject, INT2FIX(-1));
5537  ADD_SEND(ret, line, idAREF, INT2FIX(1));
5538  ADD_INSN1(ret, line, setn, FIXNUM_INC(argc, 2));
5539  ADD_INSN (ret, line, pop);
5540  }
5541  else {
5542  ADD_INSN1(ret, line, setn, FIXNUM_INC(argc, 1));
5543  }
5544  }
5545  else {
5546  ADD_SEQ(ret, recv);
5547  ADD_SEQ(ret, args);
5548  }
5549  ADD_SEND_WITH_FLAG(ret, line, node->nd_mid, argc, INT2FIX(flag));
5550  ADD_INSN(ret, line, pop);
5551 
5552  break;
5553  }
5554  case NODE_PRELUDE:{
5555  COMPILE_POPED(ret, "prelude", node->nd_head);
5556  COMPILE_(ret, "body", node->nd_body, poped);
5557  break;
5558  }
5559  case NODE_LAMBDA:{
5560  /* compile same as lambda{...} */
5561  VALUE block = NEW_CHILD_ISEQVAL(node->nd_body, make_name_for_block(iseq), ISEQ_TYPE_BLOCK, line);
5562  VALUE argc = INT2FIX(0);
5563  ADD_INSN1(ret, line, putspecialobject, INT2FIX(VM_SPECIAL_OBJECT_VMCORE));
5564  ADD_CALL_WITH_BLOCK(ret, line, idLambda, argc, block);
5565 
5566  if (poped) {
5567  ADD_INSN(ret, line, pop);
5568  }
5569  break;
5570  }
5571  default:
5572  rb_bug("iseq_compile_each: unknown node: %s", ruby_node_name(type));
5573  return COMPILE_NG;
5574  }
5575 
5576  /* check & remove redundant trace(line) */
5577  if (saved_last_element && ret /* ret can be 0 when error */ &&
5578  ret->last == saved_last_element &&
5579  ((INSN *)saved_last_element)->insn_id == BIN(trace)) {
5580  POP_ELEMENT(ret);
5581  }
5582 
5583  debug_node_end();
5584  return COMPILE_OK;
5585 }

1832  * ...

1845  * LABEL:
1846  * =>
1847  * LABEL:
1848  */

1850  }

1853  OPERAND_AT(iobj, 0) = OPERAND_AT(diobj, 0);

1856  }

1863  * =>
1864  * leave

1596  }

1599  break;
1600  case TS_GENTRY:

1602  struct rb_global_entry *entry =
1603  (struct rb_global_entry *)(operands[j] & (~1));
1604  generated_iseq[pos + 1 + j] = (VALUE)entry;
1605  }
1606  break;
1607  case TS_FUNCPTR:

1615  return 0;
1616  }
1617  }

1620  line_info_table[k].position = pos;
1621  k++;
1622  }

1625  }

1631  }

1634  }

2251  case SCS_AB:
2252  state = SCS_AX;
2253  break;
2254  case SCS_BA:
2255  state = SCS_BX;
2256  break;
2257  case SCS_XX:
2258  goto normal_insn;
2259  default:
2260  rb_compile_error(RSTRING_PTR(iseq->location.path), iobj->line_no,
2261  "unreachable");
2262  }
2263  /* remove useless pop */
2264  REMOVE_ELEM(list);
2265  list = list->next;
2266  goto redo_point;
2267  }
2268  default:;
2269  /* none */
2270  } /* end of switch */
2271  normal_insn:
2272  state = insn_set_sc_state(iseq, iobj, state);
2273  break;
2274  }
2275  case ISEQ_ELEMENT_LABEL:
2276  {
2277  LABEL *lobj;
2278  lobj = (LABEL *)list;
2279 
2280  state = label_set_sc_state(lobj, state);
2281  }
2282  default:
2283  break;
2284  }
2285  list = list->next;
2286  }
2287 #endif
2288  return COMPILE_OK;
2289 }

471 {
472  DECL_ANCHOR(ret);
473  rb_iseq_t *iseq;
474  INIT_ANCHOR(ret);
475  GetISeqPtr(self, iseq);
476 
477  if (node == 0) {
478  COMPILE(ret, "nil", node);
479  iseq_set_local_table(iseq, 0);
480  }
481  else if (nd_type(node) == NODE_SCOPE) {
482  /* iseq type of top, method, class, block */
483  iseq_set_local_table(iseq, node->nd_tbl);
484  iseq_set_arguments(iseq, ret, node->nd_args);
485 
486  switch (iseq->type) {
487  case ISEQ_TYPE_BLOCK:
488  {
489  LABEL *start = iseq->compile_data->start_label = NEW_LABEL(0);
490  LABEL *end = iseq->compile_data->end_label = NEW_LABEL(0);
491 
492  ADD_TRACE(ret, FIX2INT(iseq->location.first_lineno), RUBY_EVENT_B_CALL);
493  ADD_LABEL(ret, start);
494  COMPILE(ret, "block body", node->nd_body);
495  ADD_LABEL(ret, end);
496  ADD_TRACE(ret, nd_line(node), RUBY_EVENT_B_RETURN);
497 
498  /* wide range catch handler must put at last */
499  ADD_CATCH_ENTRY(CATCH_TYPE_REDO, start, end, 0, start);
500  ADD_CATCH_ENTRY(CATCH_TYPE_NEXT, start, end, 0, end);
501  break;
502  }
503  case ISEQ_TYPE_CLASS:
504  {
505  ADD_TRACE(ret, FIX2INT(iseq->location.first_lineno), RUBY_EVENT_CLASS);
506  COMPILE(ret, "scoped node", node->nd_body);
507  ADD_TRACE(ret, nd_line(node), RUBY_EVENT_END);
508  break;
509  }
510  case ISEQ_TYPE_METHOD:
511  {
512  ADD_TRACE(ret, FIX2INT(iseq->location.first_lineno), RUBY_EVENT_CALL);
513  COMPILE(ret, "scoped node", node->nd_body);
514  ADD_TRACE(ret, nd_line(node), RUBY_EVENT_RETURN);
515  break;
516  }
517  default: {
518  COMPILE(ret, "scoped node", node->nd_body);
519  break;
520  }
521  }
522  }
523  else if (RB_TYPE_P((VALUE)node, T_IMEMO)) {
524  const struct vm_ifunc *ifunc = (struct vm_ifunc *)node;
525  /* user callback */
526  (*ifunc->func)(iseq, ret, ifunc->data);
527  }
528  else {
529  switch (iseq->type) {
530  case ISEQ_TYPE_METHOD:
531  case ISEQ_TYPE_CLASS:
532  case ISEQ_TYPE_BLOCK:
533  case ISEQ_TYPE_EVAL:
534  case ISEQ_TYPE_MAIN:
535  case ISEQ_TYPE_TOP:
536  rb_compile_error(ERROR_ARGS "compile/should not be reached: %s:%d",
537  __FILE__, __LINE__);
538  break;
539  case ISEQ_TYPE_RESCUE:
540  iseq_set_exception_local_table(iseq);
541  COMPILE(ret, "rescue", node);
542  break;
543  case ISEQ_TYPE_ENSURE:
544  iseq_set_exception_local_table(iseq);
545  COMPILE_POPED(ret, "ensure", node);
546  break;
547  case ISEQ_TYPE_DEFINED_GUARD:
548  iseq_set_local_table(iseq, 0);
549  COMPILE(ret, "defined guard", node);
550  break;
551  default:
552  rb_bug("unknown scope");
553  }
554  }
555 
556  if (iseq->type == ISEQ_TYPE_RESCUE || iseq->type == ISEQ_TYPE_ENSURE) {
557  ADD_INSN2(ret, 0, getlocal, INT2FIX(2), INT2FIX(0));
558  ADD_INSN1(ret, 0, throw, INT2FIX(0) /* continue throw */ );
559  }
560  else {
561  ADD_INSN(ret, iseq->compile_data->last_line, leave);
562  }
563 
564 #if SUPPORT_JOKE
565  if (iseq->compile_data->labels_table) {
566  validate_labels(iseq, iseq->compile_data->labels_table);
567  }
568 #endif

570 }
